Package: fftwtools
Version: 0.9-1 
Date: 2013-03-02
Title: fftwtools
Author: Karim Rahim <karim.rahim@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Karim Rahim <karim.rahim@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.15.2)
Suggests: fftw
Description: This package is a wrapper for certain fftw function. Please see the fftw package for addtional tools. This package provides access to two-dimensional fft, multivariate fft, and one-dimensional real to complex fft using fftw3. The fft functions can be specified to not return the Hermitian conjugate of real data, and the one-dimensional, and multivariate fft functions can be inverted without using the Hermitian conjugate. Please see the package fftw for general one-dimensional use of fftw, the discrete cosine transform, and more detailed use of plans when using fftw.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: http://github.com/krahim/fftwtools